627
00:51:06,700 --> 00:51:08,510
I see.

628
00:51:08,510 --> 00:51:10,890
As for this, let's see.

629
00:51:11,690 --> 00:51:13,270
And...

630
00:51:13,270 --> 00:51:15,930
