667
00:54:19,550 --> 00:54:21,080
I don't want to.

668
00:54:21,080 --> 00:54:23,060
I said I don't want to.

669
00:54:26,960 --> 00:54:28,930
Ahjumma, where are you going?

670
00:54:28,930 --> 00:54:32,020
Oppa can play at our house, right?

